{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922/comments/58951557.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922/_/diff#comment-58951557"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2922, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922"}}, "title": "Stop the world from a plugin"}, "content": {"raw": "Interesting, thanks for the pull request. It would be great to also add an example (system?) plugin which stops the world, and a test where that is triggered. Sounds reasonable?\n\nI'd also be curious to know how you're using this. Are you able to start a new world after a world is stopped?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Interesting, thanks for the pull request. It would be great to also add an example (system?) plugin which stops the world, and a test where that is triggered. Sounds reasonable?</p>\n<p>I'd also be curious to know how you're using this. Are you able to start a new world after a world is stopped?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-03-15T14:48:53.661391+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": "2018-03-15T14:48:53.665535+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 58951557}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922/comments/59093233.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922/_/diff#comment-59093233"}}, "parent": {"id": 58951557, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922/comments/58951557.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922/_/diff#comment-58951557"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2922, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922"}}, "title": "Stop the world from a plugin"}, "content": {"raw": "We could add a system plugin example.\n\nIn our case, we use a world plugin which communicates with a docker-like tool for our drone firmwares. Whenever something bad happens with the firmwares, the plugin stops the world. We never restart the world after it has been stopped, we just quit gazebo, so I don't know if that works. Stopping the world ultimately destroys the world plugins so it won't work in our case, but it should work in a system plugin.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>We could add a system plugin example.</p>\n<p>In our case, we use a world plugin which communicates with a docker-like tool for our drone firmwares. Whenever something bad happens with the firmwares, the plugin stops the world. We never restart the world after it has been stopped, we just quit gazebo, so I don't know if that works. Stopping the world ultimately destroys the world plugins so it won't work in our case, but it should work in a system plugin.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-03-16T17:47:38.029301+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Olivier Crave", "uuid": "{c2c9ac10-3ca6-45ef-a19b-d3a76d065296}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc2c9ac10-3ca6-45ef-a19b-d3a76d065296%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc2c9ac10-3ca6-45ef-a19b-d3a76d065296%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a4e0f2b75ca0affe5c82b9650a623d0dd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsOC-4.png"}}, "nickname": "ocrave", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:24cd6b3d-30bb-4c42-9e4b-f5836c392874"}, "updated_on": "2018-03-16T17:47:38.097689+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 59093233}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922/comments/60010742.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922/_/diff#comment-60010742"}}, "parent": {"id": 58951557, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922/comments/58951557.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922/_/diff#comment-58951557"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2922, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922"}}, "title": "Stop the world from a plugin"}, "content": {"raw": "I added a system plugin example that you can try like so:\n\n`gzserver -s plugins/libStopWorldPlugin.so`\n\nUnfortunately, once the world is stopped, it can't be restarted from a plugin because we leave the while loop in Server::Run\\(\\) and enter gazebo shutdown procedure. This pull request is still useful to stop the world gracefully from within a plugin.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I added a system plugin example that you can try like so:</p>\n<p><code>gzserver -s plugins/libStopWorldPlugin.so</code></p>\n<p>Unfortunately, once the world is stopped, it can't be restarted from a plugin because we leave the while loop in Server::Run() and enter gazebo shutdown procedure. This pull request is still useful to stop the world gracefully from within a plugin.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-03-27T15:11:50.121108+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Olivier Crave", "uuid": "{c2c9ac10-3ca6-45ef-a19b-d3a76d065296}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc2c9ac10-3ca6-45ef-a19b-d3a76d065296%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc2c9ac10-3ca6-45ef-a19b-d3a76d065296%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a4e0f2b75ca0affe5c82b9650a623d0dd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsOC-4.png"}}, "nickname": "ocrave", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:24cd6b3d-30bb-4c42-9e4b-f5836c392874"}, "updated_on": "2018-03-27T15:11:50.185820+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 60010742}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922/comments/60012945.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922/_/diff#comment-60012945"}}, "parent": {"id": 60010742, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922/comments/60010742.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922/_/diff#comment-60010742"}}, "depth": 2}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2922, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2922.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2922"}}, "title": "Stop the world from a plugin"}, "content": {"raw": "Thanks! Pull request #2511 should prevent shutdown, I don't know if it's been ported to default yet.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Thanks! <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2511/dont-shut-down-gazebo-when-removing-a\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">Pull request #2511</a> should prevent shutdown, I don't know if it's been ported to default yet.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-03-27T15:26:19.903339+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nick